snippet: Six explosions hit neighborhoods across Baghdad on Thursday, breaking a period of relative calm in the city.
abstract: Six explosions hit neighborhoods across Baghdad, killing at least 17 people and wounding dozens, breaking a period of relative calm in the city.
lead_paragraph: Six explosions hit neighborhoods across Baghdad on Thursday, breaking a period of relative calm in the city.

headline.main: Iraq: Bombs Kill at Least 17 in Baghdad
headline.print_headline: Iraq: Bombs Kill at Least 17 in Baghdad
